1
00:00:26,740 --> 00:00:29,730
♪Memory is like reflection in the mirror♪

2
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:32,790
♪Ephemeral yet lasting in the heart♪

3
00:00:32,790 --> 00:00:36,110
♪I let go of worries and face the road ahead♪

4
00:00:36,110 --> 00:00:39,410
♪The vast land stretches far and wide♪

5
00:00:39,410 --> 00:00:42,400
♪My heart remains strong, spirit unbroken♪

6
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:45,540
♪May this life remain unscathed,
till we meet again♪

7
00:00:45,540 --> 00:00:48,880
♪With calm laughter, I vanquish evil♪

8
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:52,030
♪Together, we walk through life hand in hand♪

9
00:00:52,190 --> 00:00:55,480
♪Dust rises♪

10
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:58,280
♪The melody continues amidst the turmoil♪

11
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:02,910
♪We stand firm in the wind side by side♪

12
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:06,740
♪I dream as if all is but a fleeting moment♪

13
00:01:06,740 --> 00:01:09,180
♪Yet life rarely follows our desires♪

14
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:15,520
♪With the totem of strength,
I endure many trials♪

15
00:01:15,890 --> 00:01:19,460
♪Cross love and hate, life and death♪

16
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:22,240
♪We fight with heads held high♪

17
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:26,040
♪Facing the chasm of life♪

18
00:01:26,290 --> 00:01:30,610
♪We stand tall fearlessly♪

19
00:01:30,860 --> 00:01:35,980
=Fateful Love=

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,980
=Episode 3=

21
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,480
Father, you summoned me urgently.

22
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,090
Could it be

23
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:45,840
that you just want me to play chess
with you?

24
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:53,450
Has the matter of selecting a consort
been settled?

25
00:01:56,090 --> 00:01:56,930
Yes.

26
00:01:59,130 --> 00:01:59,970
Which family's young lady

27
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,280
was chosen?

28
00:02:05,730 --> 00:02:06,570
Father.

29
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,360
Why do you ask
when you've already known the answer?

30
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:14,240
Haven't you been asking me

31
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,690
to marry with Chancellor Han's daughter?

32
00:02:16,850 --> 00:02:17,690
I will

33
00:02:19,330 --> 00:02:20,240
comply with it.

34
00:02:24,050 --> 00:02:25,160
It sounds

35
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,490
that

36
00:02:28,570 --> 00:02:30,080
you are somewhat unwilling.

37
00:02:34,930 --> 00:02:36,330
No, I'm not.

38
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:40,570
But the person you chose

39
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,720
is truly unexpected.

40
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:49,920
Father.

41
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,690
Since I have already complied with

42
00:02:52,690 --> 00:02:53,570
your wish

43
00:02:54,410 --> 00:02:55,720
to marry Chancellor Han's daughter.

44
00:02:56,690 --> 00:02:58,850
As for choosing which daughter

45
00:02:58,850 --> 00:02:59,990
from the Chancellor Han's Mansion,

46
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:02,720
can I make my own decision?

47
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,930
Play chess then.

48
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:19,020
(Tianqi)

49
00:03:26,690 --> 00:03:27,530
Shadow.

50
00:03:28,410 --> 00:03:29,250
Gu.

51
00:03:30,850 --> 00:03:31,690
Where is His Highness?

52
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,800
He has been inside for quite a while

53
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,880
and still hasn't come out.

54
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:36,720
I'm also anxious.

55
00:03:37,490 --> 00:03:38,330
Let me tell you.

56
00:03:39,290 --> 00:03:40,490
His Highness has caused trouble.

57
00:03:41,290 --> 00:03:42,210
With his temperament,

58
00:03:42,850 --> 00:03:44,690
he won't come out
without some punishment.

59
00:03:46,210 --> 00:03:47,410
Well, I just don't understand.

60
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,850
Although that woman was poisoned
because of His Highness,

61
00:03:51,410 --> 00:03:53,130
there was no need to marry her.

62
00:03:55,050 --> 00:03:57,410
Then you have misunderstood

63
00:03:57,410 --> 00:03:59,490
His Highness's intentions.

64
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:00,970
What do you mean?

65
00:04:03,570 --> 00:04:04,410
Think about it.

66
00:04:05,210 --> 00:04:07,570
Moxun is a rare poison in the world.

67
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,160
That woman was poisoned

68
00:04:09,850 --> 00:04:11,600
yet she is living well.

69
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:13,880
There must be something important
behind this.

70
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,080
With His Highness's character,

71
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,760
how could he
not investigate it thoroughly?

72
00:04:21,970 --> 00:04:23,040
That makes sense.

73
00:04:24,410 --> 00:04:26,290
Moreover, that woman has even fought
with His Highness.

74
00:04:26,290 --> 00:04:28,040
Her martial arts are quite impressive.

75
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:32,570
(Tianqi)
About why such a concubine's daughter

76
00:04:32,570 --> 00:04:33,990
has such skills, we must find out the truth.

77
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,800
Keeping her close
will be more convenient indeed.

78
00:04:50,010 --> 00:04:51,290
This move in chess is not good.

79
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,040
Just change it.

80
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:07,610
You are

81
00:05:07,610 --> 00:05:09,800
still as stubborn as
when you were a child.

82
00:05:11,690 --> 00:05:12,920
As long as you are determined,

83
00:05:13,890 --> 00:05:15,200
even if you've known it's wrong,

84
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,240
you resolutely refuse to change.

85
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,800
Listen to me.

86
00:05:24,450 --> 00:05:25,410
Change it.

87
00:05:26,010 --> 00:05:26,850
Otherwise,

88
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,730
you will surely lose.

89
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:38,850
I have not lost yet.

90
00:05:42,130 --> 00:05:43,360
This is just the beginning.

91
00:05:49,350 --> 00:05:50,700
Will you change it or not?

92
00:05:53,690 --> 00:05:55,010
The pieces are scattered,

93
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,040
so the outcome is already decided.

94
00:06:00,130 --> 00:06:00,970
Father,

95
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,080
how can this be changed?

96
00:06:07,410 --> 00:06:08,520
Beiyue,

97
00:06:10,010 --> 00:06:12,890
if you don't like that Han Xi'er,

98
00:06:13,450 --> 00:06:15,760
you can make her a concubine.

99
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,290
I will not oppose it.

100
00:06:17,890 --> 00:06:18,730
But you

101
00:06:19,450 --> 00:06:22,610
insist on marrying an infamous girl.

102
00:06:24,570 --> 00:06:25,640
You are deliberately

103
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,920
bringing shame
to the Tianque royal family.

104
00:06:28,730 --> 00:06:29,890
Jun Beiyue,

105
00:06:29,890 --> 00:06:31,890
what are your true intentions?

106
00:06:36,890 --> 00:06:38,130
I like her.

107
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,410
You…

108
00:06:46,170 --> 00:06:47,010
Someone!

109
00:06:48,410 --> 00:06:49,290
Your Majesty.

110
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,080
Lock him up for me.

111
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,240
Starve him for a few days first.

112
00:06:53,410 --> 00:06:55,040
Your Majesty, this is not appropriate.

113
00:06:56,290 --> 00:06:57,690
If you dare to plead for him,

114
00:06:57,690 --> 00:06:58,640
I'll lock you up too.

115
00:07:10,010 --> 00:07:10,970
No need to trouble you.

116
00:07:11,970 --> 00:07:12,810
I'll go myself.

117
00:07:16,010 --> 00:07:17,290
Starve him for a few days first.

118
00:07:17,290 --> 00:07:18,200
If he doesn't change,

119
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,640
he can never come back.

120
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:21,160
Yes, Your Majesty.

121
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:32,610
Your Majesty.

122
00:07:32,610 --> 00:07:34,480
Please stop stepping around.

123
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,640
Sit down and calm your anger.

124
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,040
Please sit.

125
00:07:42,450 --> 00:07:43,640
Your Majesty,

126
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,970
take it easy.

127
00:07:44,970 --> 00:07:46,240
Don't harm your health.

128
00:07:49,170 --> 00:07:50,010
Take it easy?

129
00:07:52,970 --> 00:07:56,170
Because of the few military achievements
he has made over the years,

130
00:07:56,690 --> 00:07:59,240
he has been disregarding me.

131
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,240
How can I take it easy?

132
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,320
Your Majesty,

133
00:08:04,010 --> 00:08:06,450
isn't it because you have
overly favored him?

134
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,800
Moreover,

135
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:11,690
the Fourth Prince
has unparalleled achievements,

136
00:08:11,690 --> 00:08:13,760
and he has kept Tianque in peace.

137
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,970
Your Majesty,

138
00:08:20,970 --> 00:08:22,890
but on the other hand,

139
00:08:22,890 --> 00:08:24,690
if we give Beichen a chance,

140
00:08:25,410 --> 00:08:27,130
he might not lose much.

141
00:08:30,730 --> 00:08:31,570
Beichen.

142
00:08:33,490 --> 00:08:35,930
You know how capable Beichen is.

143
00:08:39,050 --> 00:08:40,290
He is not good

144
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,170
at leading troops,

145
00:08:42,170 --> 00:08:44,000
but does well at forming factions.

146
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,200
Your Majesty,

147
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:48,520
now it's Beiyue who has upset you.

148
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,730
Why bring Beichen into this?

149
00:08:51,250 --> 00:08:52,090
Moreover,

150
00:08:52,610 --> 00:08:54,760
you wanted Beiyue
to marry Chancellor Han's daughter.

151
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,170
That was originally a kind gesture.

152
00:08:56,730 --> 00:08:58,680
But he didn't have to bring back
an infamous woman.

153
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:01,680
He deliberately chose such a woman.

154
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:04,080
That was clearly to oppose you.

155
00:09:07,370 --> 00:09:08,520
Alright, alright.

156
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,360
Stop talking.

157
00:09:14,580 --> 00:09:18,880
This still requires you
to personally handle it.

158
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:19,880
Your Majesty, rest assured.

159
00:09:20,410 --> 00:09:22,120
For the prestige of the royal family,

160
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,680
I will have to play the villain.

161
00:09:25,490 --> 00:09:28,080
You understand me best.

162
00:09:29,930 --> 00:09:30,770
Your Majesty.

163
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,490
Will the Fourth Prince return tonight?

164
00:09:36,490 --> 00:09:37,640
I don't know.

165
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,850
But His Highness never stays overnight
in the palace.

166
00:09:39,850 --> 00:09:40,990
- He should be coming back.
- Cui'er.

167
00:09:46,050 --> 00:09:47,760
Watch your mouth.

168
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,810
You are so talkative.

169
00:09:48,810 --> 00:09:49,650
I might as well mute you.

170
00:09:50,490 --> 00:09:51,640
Hongyi,

171
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:52,930
Princess Consort asked me that.

172
00:09:52,930 --> 00:09:54,370
Since when is she a Princess Consort?

173
00:09:54,370 --> 00:09:55,440
You call her so affectionately.

174
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:56,960
Leave.

175
00:09:57,170 --> 00:09:58,010
Yes.

176
00:09:59,260 --> 00:10:00,120
Miss Han,

177
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,490
you'd better not wait.

178
00:10:01,490 --> 00:10:03,490
The Fourth Prince is busy
with official duties.

179
00:10:03,490 --> 00:10:05,640
Even if he returns, he won't have time
to come over.

180
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,000
Alright, I understand.

181
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:08,840
You may leave.

182
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:15,600
Wait.

183
00:10:18,490 --> 00:10:19,330
I'm hungry.

184
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:20,400
Get me something to eat.

185
00:10:25,970 --> 00:10:26,810
Hongyi.

186
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,040
What is it?

187
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,680
Someone from Yiqing Palace is here.

188
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,520
Yiqing Palace?

189
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,560
It's almost dark.

190
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,520
What are they here for?

191
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,520
I'm not quite sure.

192
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:37,250
The Queen has issued a decree.

193
00:10:37,250 --> 00:10:39,930
She invites Miss Han to the palace.

194
00:10:40,610 --> 00:10:41,680
But His Highness has ordered

195
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,000
that Miss Han is not allowed to leave.

196
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:44,400
Hongyi,

197
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,410
do you dare to defy the decree?

198
00:10:46,870 --> 00:10:49,350
(The Queen has always been at odds
with His Highness.)

199
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:52,100
(It's not worth offending her
over Han Ziqing.)

200
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,560
(If something really happens,
it would be good.)

201
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:56,640
(It would just get rid of this woman)

202
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:58,830
(and save His Highness
from being ridiculed.)

203
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:02,610
(Moreover, it would provide an excuse
to trouble the Queen.)

204
00:11:03,170 --> 00:11:04,760
(Killing three birds with one stone.)

205
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:05,850
(Why not do it?)

206
00:11:06,610 --> 00:11:07,610
I dare not.

207
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:08,640
I'll get the carriage ready now.

208
00:11:12,970 --> 00:11:13,810
Miss Han.

209
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,250
Then let's have a meal at Yiqing Palace.

210
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:18,960
Let's go.

211
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:23,960
Stop right there.

212
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,040
This has nothing to do with you.

213
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,760
You were suddenly summoned
to the palace.

214
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:46,850
Aren't you afraid at all?

215
00:11:47,970 --> 00:11:48,930
What should I be afraid of?

216
00:11:50,930 --> 00:11:53,610
Yiqing Palace is not a simple place.

217
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:57,050
It's easy to go in but hard to leave.

218
00:11:57,050 --> 00:11:57,890
Is that so?

219
00:11:58,680 --> 00:11:59,850
I'm even more looking forward to it.

220
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,760
You do have some courage.

221
00:12:04,410 --> 00:12:05,560
I underestimated you before.

222
00:12:08,050 --> 00:12:10,050
The Queen is summoning me
to the palace at this time.

223
00:12:10,050 --> 00:12:10,890
What could it be?

224
00:12:11,970 --> 00:12:13,640
What else could it be?

225
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:15,410
It's to give our mansion a hard time.

226
00:12:17,490 --> 00:12:18,330
A hard time?

227
00:12:20,290 --> 00:12:22,880
She had a grudge
against the Fourth Prince?

228
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:26,000
The Fourth Prince's reputation
is widespread,

229
00:12:26,590 --> 00:12:29,050
and the Queen has long seen him

230
00:12:29,050 --> 00:12:30,680
as a thorn in her side.

231
00:12:31,370 --> 00:12:33,730
She's afraid he will block the path
of the Second Prince Jun Beichen.

232
00:12:34,370 --> 00:12:35,560
In recent years,

233
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:37,640
the Ouyang Family
has been gaining momentum,

234
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:39,610
and with her brother General Ouyang

235
00:12:39,610 --> 00:12:41,000
backing her up,

236
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,850
she can no longer tolerate His Highness.

237
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,370
And now,

238
00:12:45,370 --> 00:12:47,850
the Fourth Prince has allied with
the Chancellor's Mansion by marriage.

239
00:12:48,490 --> 00:12:50,370
She naturally won't be happy.

240
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,040
I see.

241
00:12:54,490 --> 00:12:55,330
So,

242
00:12:56,290 --> 00:12:58,170
she's picking on me as the easy target.

243
00:12:59,060 --> 00:13:06,060
(Tianqi)

244
00:13:30,630 --> 00:13:31,550
When you get to the palace,

245
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:32,650
mind your manners.

246
00:13:37,850 --> 00:13:38,850
You'll suffer.

247
00:13:38,850 --> 00:13:42,420
(Tianqi)

248
00:13:57,250 --> 00:13:58,490
Jingqin,

249
00:13:58,490 --> 00:14:01,810
did your father like the tea
I gave him yesterday?

250
00:14:01,810 --> 00:14:03,880
The tea you chose is always excellent,

251
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:05,610
so my father naturally likes it.

252
00:14:05,610 --> 00:14:07,250
Your Majesty and General Ouyang

253
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:09,290
truly share a deep sibling bond.

254
00:14:09,290 --> 00:14:10,320
General Ouyang

255
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:12,290
has made great contributions to Tianque,

256
00:14:12,290 --> 00:14:14,680
and recently quelled
the southern rebellion.

257
00:14:14,680 --> 00:14:16,200
I believe His Majesty will

258
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:17,930
reward him handsomely again this time.

259
00:14:19,610 --> 00:14:21,640
The General's Mansion indeed has merits,

260
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:23,080
but where do you

261
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:25,080
put the Mansion of Fourth Prince at?

262
00:14:25,760 --> 00:14:27,410
After all, the Fourth Prince is still young.

263
00:14:27,930 --> 00:14:30,120
How could he be as mature and steady
as the General?

264
00:14:30,730 --> 00:14:32,050
The grand scheme of Tianque

265
00:14:32,050 --> 00:14:34,760
still requires an experienced general
like General Ouyang

266
00:14:34,760 --> 00:14:37,290
to assist His Majesty.

267
00:14:37,290 --> 00:14:38,130
Indeed.

268
00:14:38,970 --> 00:14:40,760
Your Majesty, Han Ziqing has arrived.

269
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:05,320
Greetings, Your Majesty.

270
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:08,730
She doesn't understand the rules at all.

271
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:11,930
She didn't perform the kneeling ceremony
when greeting Her Majesty.

272
00:15:11,930 --> 00:15:14,320
Who knows if she doesn't understand,

273
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,410
or if she is unwilling?

274
00:15:18,730 --> 00:15:20,250
I have lived a secluded life,

275
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:22,080
and don't know the palace rules.

276
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:25,810
As the saying goes, ignorance
is not to be blamed.

277
00:15:25,810 --> 00:15:27,120
Your Majesty, as the mother of the nation,

278
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:30,290
wouldn't be harsh over such matters, right?

279
00:15:40,370 --> 00:15:41,970
(Are they forcing me to kneel?)

280
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,370
(This girl is not simple.)

281
00:15:47,640 --> 00:15:49,760
