297
00:16:37,490 --> 00:16:39,680
This is the younger sister.

298
00:16:40,490 --> 00:16:41,330
The younger sister?

299
00:16:43,170 --> 00:16:44,080
How is that possible?

300
00:16:45,050 --> 00:16:47,520
I heard that the sister

301
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,640
is a…

302
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:51,080
An infamous girl.

303
00:16:51,640 --> 00:16:54,170
When in Grandeur Palace…

304
00:16:54,170 --> 00:16:55,760
So it was her.

305
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:59,000
How can this be acceptable?

306
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:01,810
Has the Fourth Prince been bewitched
by her?

307
00:17:01,810 --> 00:17:03,080
- I think so too.
- Exactly.

308
00:17:05,370 --> 00:17:06,970
(I thought it was a big trap.)

309
00:17:07,850 --> 00:17:09,680
(But it's just a bunch of gossip ladies.)

310
00:17:10,800 --> 00:17:12,490
In my opinion,

311
00:17:12,490 --> 00:17:14,800
there must be some misunderstanding.

312
00:17:16,010 --> 00:17:18,130
She's chosen by the Fourth Prince.

313
00:17:18,130 --> 00:17:19,680
How could she be an infamous person?

314
00:17:21,610 --> 00:17:22,450
Ziqing,

315
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:25,530
about the matter in Grandeur Palace,

316
00:17:26,370 --> 00:17:27,490
is it true?

317
00:17:29,010 --> 00:17:29,850
Your Majesty,

318
00:17:30,490 --> 00:17:31,770
- it's true.
- What?

319
00:17:32,190 --> 00:17:33,030
You…

320
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:35,890
You still have the nerve to admit it.

321
00:17:39,010 --> 00:17:39,850
Someone, come here.

322
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,560
Did the Fourth Prince really choose her?

323
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,440
Your Majesty,

324
