to hold someone accountable,

334
00:18:08,490 --> 00:18:09,850
then go ask the Fourth Prince.

335
00:18:18,850 --> 00:18:21,130
Since the Fourth Prince
personally chose you,

336
00:18:21,770 --> 00:18:24,040
he must have his reasons.

337
00:18:24,970 --> 00:18:26,680
