to interfere.

339
00:18:30,530 --> 00:18:31,920
(So you understand it.)

340
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,000
Your Majesty is too kind.

341
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:35,520
Come on,

342
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:37,530
Ziqing.

343
00:18:37,530 --> 00:18:39,010
Today I invited you here

344
00:18:39,530 --> 00:18:41,040
