to be the Princess Consort.)

352
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:18,530
You are too restrained.

353
00:19:26,610 --> 00:19:27,450
Come here.

354
00:19:28,190 --> 00:19:30,820
I will personally serve you tea.

355
00:19:37,850 --> 00:19:38,800
Ziqing,

356
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,200
Mother treats you well.

357
00:19:42,040 --> 00:19:43,610
You should not refuse her kindness.

358
00:19:46,450 --> 00:19:48,010
Since Your Majesty
is personally serving tea,

359
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:49,970
