360
00:19:51,730 --> 00:19:52,570
Thank you.

361
00:19:57,730 --> 00:19:59,370
(If you're playing tricks,
I'll play with you.)

362
00:19:59,970 --> 00:20:00,810
(Since you want to act,)

363
00:20:01,610 --> 00:20:02,800
(why not make it real?)

364
00:20:12,370 --> 00:20:13,530
How does it taste?

365
00:20:15,320 --> 00:20:17,370
This tea has a strong color and aroma.

366
00:20:18,560 --> 00:20:19,560
Although it's autumn tea,

367
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:22,890
it is not inferior to the taste
of spring tea.

368
00:20:24,770 --> 00:20:26,530
I didn't expect that you know about tea.

369
00:20:29,250 --> 00:20:31,920
Alright, it's getting late.

370
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:34,200
Everyone should probably rest now.

371
00:20:35,320 --> 00:20:36,160
Ziqing,

372
00:20:36,850 --> 00:20:38,250
I won't keep you any longer.

373
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,680
Thank you for your hospitality,
Your Majesty.

374
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:42,490
By the way, Ziqing,

375
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:44,800
there's something I forgot to tell you.

376
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:47,920
His Majesty values the Fourth Prince,

377
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,320
so before the selection of the consort,

378
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:51,850
he had discussed it with Chancellor Han.

379
00:20:52,610 --> 00:20:55,890
On the fourth day of next month, they will
go your home to announce the engagement.

380
00:20:56,920 --> 00:21:00,200
There are only seven days left.

381
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:04,400
You should go back and prepare well.

382
00:21:06,370 --> 00:21:09,010
(No wonder you chose a slow poison
like Huajin.)

383
00:21:09,850 --> 00:21:11,560
(The poison will take effect
in seven days.)

384
00:21:11,560 --> 00:21:12,990
(The decree will be announced
in seven days.)

385
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:16,530
(So the auspicious day you chose)

386
00:21:16,530 --> 00:21:17,920
(is actually my death day.)

387
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,610
(I must expel the poison quickly.)

388
00:21:36,220 --> 00:21:38,860
(Tianqi)

389
00:21:41,040 --> 00:21:42,130
You come out so quickly.

390
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:44,970
Did they give you a hard time?

391
00:21:45,730 --> 00:21:46,650
Did they do anything to you?

392
00:21:52,890 --> 00:21:54,160
Say something.

393
00:21:57,320 --> 00:21:58,160
What's wrong with you?

394
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:02,160
You, you…

395
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:05,080
- Are you okay?
- Shut up.

396
00:22:09,650 --> 00:22:11,040
If you dare to say another word,

397
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,920
I'll cut your tongue out.

398
00:22:14,790 --> 00:22:16,770
You seem like a different person.

399
00:22:40,490 --> 00:22:41,330
Move aside.

400
00:23:18,320 --> 00:23:19,680
Your Majesty,

401
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:22,130
drink this cup of tea and then rest.

402
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:28,280
Was it

403
00:23:28,610 --> 00:23:30,560
handled properly?

404
00:23:30,560 --> 00:23:31,770
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

405
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:35,080
The symptoms of Huajin Poison

406
00:23:35,080 --> 00:23:37,890
are indistinguishable from those
of tuberculosis.

407
00:23:37,890 --> 00:23:40,200
Ordinary doctors won't be able
to tell the difference.

408
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:42,800
That woman

409
00:23:42,800 --> 00:23:45,370
will only lament her misfortune.

410
00:23:45,370 --> 00:23:47,200
She has had this incurable disease,

411
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:49,530
before she could become
a princess consort.

412
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:51,920
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

413
00:23:51,920 --> 00:23:54,770
Within seven days, that woman
will surely be dead.

414
00:23:54,770 --> 00:23:57,200
You need not worry about it anymore.

415
00:24:07,370 --> 00:24:08,370
Is there something on my face?

416
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:09,770
No.

417
00:24:11,530 --> 00:24:12,650
