418
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:16,160
I, I…

419
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:17,010
I don't dare.

420
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:19,400
You were the one who sent me
to Yiqing Palace.

421
00:24:20,970 --> 00:24:22,130
This poison in me

422
00:24:23,080 --> 00:24:24,080
is thanks to you.

423
00:24:24,080 --> 00:24:24,920
Your Highness,

424
00:24:27,130 --> 00:24:28,040
I

425
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:29,440
fail to recognize a great person.

426
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:31,920
Please, spare me.

427
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:32,760
I won't dare anymore.

428
00:24:34,250 --> 00:24:35,090
Won't dare what?

429
00:24:35,770 --> 00:24:38,130
I won't dare to be disrespectful
to you anymore.

430
00:24:41,370 --> 00:24:42,850
Don't look down on people anymore.

431
00:24:44,370 --> 00:24:45,210
Hongyi,

432
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:46,200
about today's matter,

433
00:24:46,800 --> 00:24:48,400
I can let it go.

434
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,440
If His Highness asks,

435
00:24:50,280 --> 00:24:51,490
I will even help you explain.

436
00:24:52,250 --> 00:24:53,770
Thank you, Your Highness.

437
00:24:54,530 --> 00:24:55,370
Don't thank me yet.

438
00:24:56,080 --> 00:24:57,040
I haven't finished speaking.

439
00:24:57,040 --> 00:24:58,680
Please give your orders, Your Highness.

440
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:01,530
About everything that happened today,

441
00:25:03,040 --> 00:25:04,040
you cannot tell anyone.

442
00:25:04,730 --> 00:25:05,970
Not even His Highness?

443
00:25:08,130 --> 00:25:10,490
The Fourth Prince and the Queen
are already at odds.

444
00:25:12,850 --> 00:25:14,530
If their conflict escalates,

445
00:25:16,040 --> 00:25:17,320
what if they start fighting?

446
00:25:18,770 --> 00:25:20,010
I see.

447
00:25:20,010 --> 00:25:20,970
I won't speak out.

448
00:25:27,010 --> 00:25:28,610
I heard that the Fourth Prince

449
00:25:29,320 --> 00:25:30,200
is quite remarkable.

450
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,160
Indeed,

451
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,440
that's the Fourth Prince.

452
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:33,770
Not just in Tianque,

453
00:25:33,770 --> 00:25:35,160
but across the entire Longyuan Continent,

454
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:37,920
whether it's Xiling, which stands
against Tianque,

455
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:39,970
Tieyan, which borders Xiling,

456
00:25:39,970 --> 00:25:42,010
the weakest Dongling,

457
00:25:42,010 --> 00:25:44,530
or the powerful Nanzhao,

458
00:25:44,530 --> 00:25:47,280
they all admire the Fourth Prince
greatly.

459
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,770
I see that the Fourth Prince

460
00:25:51,560 --> 00:25:52,920
always carries a dagger.

461
00:25:54,610 --> 00:25:55,920
That dagger is very exquisite.

462
00:25:58,130 --> 00:25:59,770
Is it his treasure?

463
00:26:00,850 --> 00:26:01,850
Since I entered the mansion,

464
00:26:01,850 --> 00:26:04,010
I've seen the dagger on his waist.

465
00:26:04,010 --> 00:26:04,970
He indeed cherishes it.

466
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:08,080
Always carries it?

467
00:26:13,320 --> 00:26:14,160
Alright.

468
00:26:14,320 --> 00:26:15,160
I see.

469
00:26:15,530 --> 00:26:16,370
Don't talk to me anymore.

470
00:26:18,320 --> 00:26:19,890
You, you…

471
00:26:19,890 --> 00:26:20,890
This

472
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:22,400
wound…

473
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:24,520
