474
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,240
Forget it.

475
00:26:31,800 --> 00:26:34,610
After tomorrow night's dinner,

476
00:26:34,610 --> 00:26:36,560
let Beiyue and the others go back.

477
00:26:36,560 --> 00:26:37,700
That's not advisable, Your Majesty.

478
00:26:38,610 --> 00:26:40,920
The Fourth Prince has many capable men
around him.

479
00:26:41,850 --> 00:26:42,970
If he goes back,

480
00:26:42,970 --> 00:26:44,680
and finds out that the woman is poisoned,

481
00:26:45,250 --> 00:26:46,850
all our efforts will be in vain.

482
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:50,610
Release him on the sixth day.

483
00:26:51,730 --> 00:26:53,200
By then,

484
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:54,970
the woman will be critically ill,

485
00:26:54,970 --> 00:26:55,920
and beyond cure.

486
00:26:57,250 --> 00:27:00,770
Even if the Fourth Prince finds out,
it won't help.

487
00:27:07,370 --> 00:27:08,590
You

488
00:27:08,590 --> 00:27:10,010
have thought it through thoroughly.

489
00:27:27,250 --> 00:27:28,090
Your Highness,

490
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:29,680
