497
00:27:42,890 --> 00:27:44,040
Quite good. Keep it up.

498
00:27:45,250 --> 00:27:46,090
Yes, Your Highness.

499
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,040
Yesterday, the Queen put on

500
00:27:48,040 --> 00:27:49,520
such a big show in front of me.

501
00:27:49,850 --> 00:27:51,160
I must repay her properly.

502
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:55,120
Is there anything else?

503
00:27:56,320 --> 00:27:58,730
The Second Princess Consort
and Miss Ouyang Jingshi have arrived.

504
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:00,760
Who?

505
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:02,490
The Queen's niece.

506
00:28:02,490 --> 00:28:04,440
Ouyang Jingqin and Ouyang Jingshi.

507
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:06,320
They are General Ouyang's daughters

508
00:28:06,320 --> 00:28:07,550
and they are biological sisters.

509
00:28:07,890 --> 00:28:08,970
Ouyang Jingqin

510
00:28:08,970 --> 00:28:10,920
married her cousin Jun Beichen.

511
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:12,920
Thus, the two families
are closely related.

512
00:28:13,650 --> 00:28:17,200
She is the Second Princess Consort
I met yesterday.

513
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,090
Exactly.

514
00:28:18,560 --> 00:28:20,440
The Second Princess Consort is good,

515
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:22,250
but her sister Ouyang Jingshi

516
00:28:22,250 --> 00:28:24,400
is notoriously arrogant and spoiled.

517
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:27,020
But His Majesty is very fond of her.

518
00:28:27,500 --> 00:28:29,660
If it weren't for her
being from the General's Mansion,

519
00:28:29,670 --> 00:28:31,760
