has always been dissatisfied

523
00:28:38,770 --> 00:28:40,690
with the marriage alliance
between our two mansions.

524
00:28:41,060 --> 00:28:43,500
These two sisters must be here
to cause trouble.

525
00:28:43,890 --> 00:28:44,990
What should we do?

526
00:28:48,990 --> 00:28:50,240
It's a good chance to test the medicine.

527
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:51,760
Come on,

528
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:53,000
change the clothes for me.

529
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:03,400
