530
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:05,200
making us wait here.

531
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:06,320
We are guests,

532
00:29:06,320 --> 00:29:07,160
and she is the host.

533
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:09,160
Waiting a bit is no big deal.

534
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:10,970
What kind of host is she?

535
00:29:11,530 --> 00:29:12,920
This is the Mansion of Fourth Prince.

536
00:29:13,490 --> 00:29:14,920
What does it have to do
with that woman?

537
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:15,760
Jingshi,

538
00:29:16,010 --> 00:29:16,850
mind your manners.

539
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:19,280
As the General's daughter,

540
00:29:19,280 --> 00:29:20,400
you should not speak so crudely.

541
00:29:22,080 --> 00:29:22,920
Sit down.

542
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:41,320
The Princess Consort has arrived.

543
00:29:42,680 --> 00:29:43,520
Slow down.

544
00:29:44,610 --> 00:29:45,450
Your Highness, be careful.

545
00:29:46,130 --> 00:29:46,970
Be careful.

546
00:29:51,130 --> 00:29:51,970
Sis.

547
00:29:53,080 --> 00:29:54,160
Aunt is right.

548
00:29:54,970 --> 00:29:57,130
This woman has been poisoned
by Huajin.

549
00:29:57,130 --> 00:29:58,970
- Slow down.
- She won't survive much longer.

550
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:04,640
Be careful.

551
00:30:06,870 --> 00:30:07,710
Your Highness.

552
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:15,610
I didn't know we had
such esteemed guests.

553
00:30:16,610 --> 00:30:17,450
I

554
00:30:19,970 --> 00:30:21,250
am gravely ill.

555
00:30:22,280 --> 00:30:23,850
Apologize for not welcoming you
properly.

556
00:30:27,770 --> 00:30:29,680
You're a concubine's daughter.

557
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:31,040
How dare you speak to us sisters.

558
00:30:32,130 --> 00:30:33,160
Shameless.

559
00:30:34,970 --> 00:30:35,970
What did you say?

560
00:30:35,970 --> 00:30:36,810
